Category.name: phone
Category.comment: This is the static phone category. It cannot be changed or removed

Category.name: whistlehack
Category.comment:
Added so we can easily do the rewrite rule:
s* >> [f* | v* | th* | dh*]
transforms to:
s* >> qt* >> [f* | v* | th* | dh*]
Now works as:
s* >> whistlehack transforms to:
s* >> qt* >> whistlehack

MainPhoneList: <Phone name="uu'" comment="We have increased the qss's because uu tends to get underestimated as it is often final and dies away. The "'" version is longer in proportion to the not-' version by rough comparison with other vowels. Yes!!! This is *very* ad hoc and Len disapproves!" >

Prototype.name: TriphoneDefault
Prototype.Equation: (qssb1 / tempo1) + (transition2 + qssa2 + qssb2) / tempo2 + (transition3 + qssa3) / tempo3

Prototype.name: TetraphoneDefault
Prototype.Equation: (qssb1 / tempo1) + (transition2 + qssa2 + qssb2) / tempo2 + (transition3 + qssa3 + qssb3) / tempo3 + (transition4 + qssa4) / tempo4

Prototype.name: Mark2
Prototype.Equation: (qssb1 / tempo1) + (transition2 + qssa2 + qssb2) / tempo2 + (transition3 + qssa3) / tempo3

Prototype.name: endOfVLessAspBurst

This is the one we are always looking for!!
Namely rd - (qssa3/2)/tempo3

Prototype.name: VStopVTotalDur

Prototype.name: vlessStopBurstTopB

Prototype.name: vlessStopBurstTopC
